WEBVTT

00:00:02.349 --> 00:00:03.913
Makes sense now, doesn't it?

00:00:03.999 --> 00:00:11.093
Yeah. We said the problem was deadlines,
then pressure, then bad reactions.

00:00:11.730 --> 00:00:15.846
But this? This was already tilted
before anyone raised their voice.

00:00:16.705 --> 00:00:19.386
Did you understand what
Priya actually decided?

00:00:19.670 --> 00:00:22.906
No. But I'm not getting
dragged into that again.

00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:26.900
Side conversations after the meeting.

00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:29.560
That's a signal.

00:00:33.799 --> 00:00:36.986
Silence during risk talk. Another signal.

00:00:38.539 --> 00:00:40.066
Pressure without ownership.

00:00:41.539 --> 00:00:44.706
Speed over clarity. All signals.